
To use the readWav.py script: Open a comand prompt and cd to be in microphone/test folder. 
Make sure correct COM port is indicated in python file
start the code on the micro controller
the led on the SD breakout should start flashing rapidly to indicate audio is being written to it

once this process has begun type python readWAV.py into the command prompt

wav file called received.wav should be generated in this folder
